QuestData.Title: Super Jiro
QuestData.Description:
The outsiders have disrupted the tasks and purpose of the jiro. We cannot allow this to continue.
We will empower a larger jiro to help combat these threats. Jiro Prime will destroy the enemies that threaten Zereth Mortis.
Help direct Jiro Prime to resolve our crisis.
QuestData.LogDescription: Direct Jiro Prime to rescue $4oa Distressed Jiro, while slaying $2oa Mawbroken Automa and $3oa Mawsworn forces.
QuestData.RewardText: Order has been restored. We thank you for your assistance.
